{
  "id": "ancient-scroll",
  "name": "古风信笺",
  "category": "ancient",
  "description": "一封古风卷轴信笺，带有印章和诗词装饰",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.03,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "setting",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "古代|古风|仙侠|武侠|宫廷|民国",
        "description": "古代或古风场景可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "date": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "日期（古代纪年格式）"
    },
    "title": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "信笺标题"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 500,
      "description": "信笺正文内容"
    },
    "poemLine1": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "诗句第一行"
    },
    "poemLine2": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "诗句第二行"
    },
    "closing": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "结语敬词"
    },
    "sender": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "署名"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一封古风信笺的内容。\n\n背景信息：\n- 写信人：{{sender}}\n- 收信人：{{recipient}}\n- 场景：{{scene}}\n- 主题：{{theme}}\n\n要求：\n1. 使用文言文或半文言文风格\n2. 内容要典雅含蓄，符合古代礼仪\n3. 可以引用或创作诗句\n4. 字数控制在200-400字之间\n5. 结尾要有敬词和署名\n\n请直接输出信笺内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "ancient",
    "colors": ["#f5e6c8", "#8b4513", "#c41e3a"],
    "mood": "典雅古韵"
  },
  "rarity": "rare",
  "collectible": true
}